			<h1 class="article-title"><a href="index.html?p=5427">《共情时代》</a></h1>
			<div class="article-meta">
				<span class="item">2019-11-07</span>
												<span class="item">分类：<a href="social-sciences/index.html" rel="category tag">社会科学</a></span>
